//  dwFlags can be set with the following 2 flags passed directly to
//  CryptFindOIDInfo:
//      CRYPT_OID_INFO_PUBKEY_SIGN_KEY_FLAG
//      CRYPT_OID_INFO_PUBKEY_ENCRYPT_KEY_FLAG
